    {
      "id": "edge-class-bridge-smoke-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Edge Class Smoke",
      "position": {
        "x": -220,
        "y": -170
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Edge Class Smoke\n\nThis graph tests the real authoring path:\n\n1. Bridge `task.depends-on`, `planning.answers`, and `graph.implements` into the host legend.\n2. Select the plain edge and assign a class in edge properties.\n3. Compare the plain edge with the class-backed edges.\n\nThe selector should offer `plain.edge` by default, then add bridged edge classes from the legend.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        },
        "_bridge": {
          "sourceNodeId": "",
          "sourceBridgeNodeId": "",
          "sourceBridgeLabel": "Migrated class binding",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "entryPort": "root",
          "kind": "node-class",
          "targetKind": "node-class",
          "classKey": "markdown",
          "classRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        },
        "definitionKey": "markdown"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "edge-class-bridge-smoke-steps",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Expected Result",
      "position": {
        "x": 420,
        "y": -170
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Expected Result\n\nAfter bridging the edge classes:\n\n- the legend should show each class entry and preview\n- edge properties should show `plain.edge` plus the bridged edge classes\n- the preassigned edge should resolve class meaning and defaults\n- selecting the plain edge should let you upgrade it to any bridged class",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node"
        },
        "_bridge": {
